- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is also likely as the paper discusses the impact of Full-duplex radios on network performance. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper proposes a new approach to improve system performance. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is relevant as the paper discusses data transmission in MIMO systems. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is less likely but still possible as the paper may touch upon security issues related to Full-duplex radios.
